Package solver.reachablepoints

Class LimitedQueue<Element>

  • java.lang.Object
    • solver.reachablepoints.LimitedQueue<Element>
  • Type Parameters:
    Element - type of the elements stored in the buffer
    public class LimitedQueue<Element>
extends Object
    Class for storing multiple elements in a buffer. The stored elements can be accessed in a queue like structure. If the buffer is filled another element gets replaced by the new one.
